   Judges' Benchbook: The Black Lung Benefits Act (2001)

          [new7.gif] In August 2001, the Office of Administrative Law
          Judges completely updated the Judges' Black Lung Benchbook,
          which was last updated in 1997. The new edition incorporates
          discussion of the new black lung regulations.

